## 2. Target audience

Jason described the target as “anyone, not specific.” Based on the business model and industry research, the practical audience breaks down like this:

- Fleet managers and operations directors at mid-to-large Canadian carriers looking to buy or sell used trailers
- Owner-operators and small fleet owners seeking quality used equipment at competitive prices
- Trucking companies looking to offload aging equipment quickly (the “we buy trailers” audience)
- Companies wanting professional fleet evaluations before making buy/sell decisions
- Businesses seeking consignment services to move equipment without doing the sales work themselves

