## 3. Inventory page requirements

The inventory page must be readily accessible and easy for the team to manage.

- **Active listings:** 5-10 groups of trailers at any time
- **Scalable:** Start with 25 open slots, with room to grow
- **Update frequency:** Roughly once a week
- **Each listing includes:** ~10 photos plus structured data fields
- **Listing fields:** Make, Year, Model, Length, Axles, Interior, Description, Price
- **Who updates:** Jason, Anthony, and Linkon all need access

**Open question:** “Groups of trailers” needs clarification. Does Jason mean one listing per individual trailer, or one listing for a batch (e.g., “5x 2019 Hyundai Translead Dry Vans”)?

